data.description: Northwest Lodge on 5 acres boasting breathtaking Mt. Rainier views. This architecturally stunning home features soaring ceilings, a dramatic floor-to-ceiling rock fireplace, and meticulous attention to detail throughout. Brazilian cherry flooring adorns the main level, while contemporary wrought iron railing adds a modern touch. The home showcases stunning 8' custom wood doors, acid stained concrete counters, warm radiant floor heating, a central vacuum system, and more. A true masterpiece of craftsmanship and design.  The bones are here, bring your touch!
